        "description": "Steady-state and transient RANS simulations of the FDA centrifugal pump at five operating points (3 L/min–4500 rpm through 7 L/min–3500 rpm). Hemolysis index computed via scalar transport of the Giersiepen-Wurzinger damage variable. Grid-convergence index reported as < 2% on HI for all cases. Results used as the primary validation evidence for the hemolysis credibility factor.",
